Ace Ventura Pet Detective 1994.
He's the best there is. In fact, he's the only one there is! He's Ace Ventura 
Pet Detective. Ace is on the case to find the Miami Dolphins' missing mascot 
and quarterback Dan Marino. He goes eyeball to eyeball with a man-eating shark, 
stakes out the Miami Dolphins and woos and wows the ladies. Whether he's 
undercover, under fire or underwater, he always gets his man or beast!

Ace Ventura When Nature Calls 1995.
Ace Ventura is back in an all-new adventure. This time an explorer named, 
Fulton Greenwall, gives him a new case in Africa to find the sacred bat of the 
Wachati and Wachootoo Tribes. It's up to Ace to find the sacred bat before the 
two tribes fight a savage war!
